  "subject": "Add ReadDataJobPerfTest for read data job classification",
  "commit_message": "Add ReadDataJobPerfTest for read data job classification\n\n- Register READY CM handles across both DMI plugins and\n  bulk non-READY handles for all classification paths\n- Test 10 selectors per request matching production\n  characteristics: 99% broadcast, 1% exact id resolution\n- Assert single request completes under 1 second\n- Assert batch of 20 parallel requests completes under\n  1 second matching 20 req/sec target\n- Log classification counts (broadcast, dmi groups,\n  notReady, errors) alongside time and memory per run\n\nIssue-ID: CPS-2887\n\nChange-Id: I520d2c0926af1341d39f06272fe138f6c6651d50\nSigned-off-by: egernug <gerard.nugent@est.tech>\n",
